---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <SectionHeading title="About" />
    <div class="about-content">
      <p class="about-hook">
        Software Engineer based in Sarajevo with 6+ years building scalable backend systems and full-stack
        applications. I specialize in .NET microservices and cloud-native architectures — from modernizing
        legacy systems to shipping real-time multiplayer games.
      </p>
      <ul class="about-bullets">
        <li>
          Expertise in <strong>Clean Architecture, DDD, and TDD</strong> — specializing in modular monoliths and event-sourced microservices with high test coverage from day one.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Backend depth</strong> across .NET 6/8 Web API, SignalR, WPF, SQL Server, MongoDB, PostgreSQL, and Jenkins CI/CD.
        </li>
        <li>
          I leverage <strong>AI-augmented workflows</strong> — including multi-agent orchestration and custom MCP servers — to accelerate the SDLC while maintaining strict TDD and Clean Architecture standards.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-hook {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-bullets {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .about-bullets li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .about-bullets li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-bullets strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
